        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 12. Chaetarthria sp. from Saudi Arabia. A–C – aedeagus (A – dorsal, B – lateral, C – ventral). D–E – habitus (D – dorsal, E – lateral). F – details of parameres and apical part of the median lobe in ventral view. G – male tergite VIII; H – male sternite VIII; I – male sternite IX; J–K – elytral setae, SEM micrographs (J – general view; K – detail)." ;
